<includeonly><span lang="ja" style="font-family: sans-serif;">{{{1}}}</span></includeonly><noinclude>
Intended for use [[wikipedia:Span_and_div|inline]] on Japanese text, wraps it with the <code>span</code> tag, sets the <code>lang</code> attribute to "ja" and <code>font-family</code> to "sans-serif".

'''Usage''':

<pre>
{{SpanJa|日本語のテキスト…}}
</pre>

'''Result''':

{{SpanJa|日本語のテキスト…}}
</noinclude>